The invention discloses a system of a high-definition digital set-top box. The system of the high-definition digital set-top box comprises a set-top box bottom layer driving module, a set-top box program management module and a set-top box application program module, wherein the set-top box bottom layer driving module comprises a front-end universal serial bus (USB), an Enthernet and software for driving a Flash and receiving remote control signals; the set-top box program management module is used for accessing and managing overall state information and user setting information, accessing, updating and managing service data, and acquiring and analyzing program data; and the set-top box application program module is used for designing and displaying a set-top box user interface and menus, applying and managing a graphical user interface, the menus or user interactive operation, and managing the development of the program management module. In the technical scheme of the invention, the system is in fit with a set-top box hardware platform to form an overall system. The system has demodulating and decoding functions and can provide a series of menu-driven graphical menus for a user.
